  "changes": [
    "Encephalon workshop testimonials commonly feature manifestation of personal symbolic objects like dragonflies during dedicated object meditations; adding 'dragonfly' as subcategory under personal_items for specificity and reusability.",
    "Merge category 'manifestation.personal_items'",
    "Further refinement to address bloat and cause-vs-effect clarity: added new 'vascular' category under healing (v7.0); moved raynauds_syndrome (to vascular), stroke (to cardiovascular), paralysis (to musculoskeletal), hernia (to digestive), perineal_tear & anal_sphincter_injury & breast_cyst (to reproductive), bone_infection (to infectious).",
    "Moved 'aneurysm' from neurological to vascular for etiological accuracy (primary vascular wall weakness, even when cerebral/carotid and neurologically symptomatic); added relevant vascular-specific attributes."
  ],
  "proposedFromVideoId": "de7qmG8CKKQ"
